description: Copilot instructions

This repository requires that any Copilot/AI assistant read and follow the directives
found in .github/agents/test-journal-logger.agent.md before taking actions.

Required steps for agents:
- Load the file [.github/agents/test-journal-logger.agent.md](.github/agents/test-journal-logger.agent.md).
- Follow its journaling and execution directives exactly.
- If the file cannot be read or its directives are unclear, request clarification and do not proceed.

Failure to follow the above means the agent must pause and ask the repository maintainer for guidance.
